  "title": "iEEG_Neural_spatial_volatility",
  "description": "This intracranial electroencephalography (iEEG) dataset contains neural recordings from patients with epilepsy, designed to investigate spatial volatility of neural activity patterns. The dataset includes raw iEEG signals acquired from implanted electrodes and is intended to support research on neural dynamics and epileptogenic zone localization.",
